NORTH
In travelling North, the player is given a directive to follow THE MUDDY FOOT PATH. In travelling North, there’s a (randomized) chance the player will meet Snakes(friend/foe).There’s a (randomized) chance the snake/s give the player clues to either; 1.  travel to the CAVES or, 2. Direct the player to the bats, or 3. continue on THE MUDDY FOOT PATH towards the SWAMP. Before reaching the SWAP the player (may/may not) find Blood (clue). This clue gives the player a (randomized) choice to either; 1. go to the CAVE where the donkey is found, or 2. go to the SWAMP where the player meets Ogre who tells the player that it is a dead end as the SWAMP is unpassable because of flesh eating fish. This means the player would be forced to go to the beginning and start again by choosing a direction.

SOUTH
In travelling South, the player is given a directive to follow THE ROCKY FOOT PATH. In travelling South, there’s a (randomized) chance the player will find Footprints (clue). There’s a (randomized) chance this clue will tell the player to either; 1. Go to the SWAMP, 2. Go to the FARM, or 3. Stay on THE ROCKY FOOT PATH that leads to FIND THE DONKEY AND WIN THE GAME. Further along THE ROCKY FOOT PATH, there’s a (randomized) chance the player will meet Bates(friend/foe) continuing to the CAVES where the donkey is found.

WEST
In travelling West, the player is given a directive to follow THE DANGEROUS OBSTACLE PATH. In travelling West, there’s a (randomized) chance the player will find Poisonous Spiders(friend/foe). There’s a (randomized) chance the Poisonous Spiders will either; 1. Attack and kill the player, 2. attack but not kill the player, 3. Do not attack the player. Further along THE DANGEROUS OBSTACLE PATH there’s a (randomized) chance the player will meet the Horse(friend/foe). There’s a (randomized) chance the Horse will either; 1. Attack and kill the player, 2. attack but not kill the player, 3. Do not attack the player. Further along THE DANGEROUS OBSTACLE PATH there’s a (randomized) chance the player will find Blood (clue). This clue gives the player a (randomized) choice to either; 1. go to the CAVE where the donkey is found, or 2. go to the TAVERN in the KINGDOM. Further along THE DANGEROUS OBSTACLE PATH there’s a (randomized) chance the player will find the donkey’s rug (clue). This clue gives the player a choice to either; 1. go to directly to the FARM bypassing the Farmer or, 2. Continue along THE DANGEROUS OBSTACLE PATH to meet the Farmer(friend/foe). If the player meets the Farmer, the Farmer tell the player to look in the CAVES for the donkey. 

EAST
In travelling East, the player is given a directive to follow GRASS & MEADOWS PATH. In travelling East, there’s a (randomized) chance the player will meet Rabbit(friend/foe). There’s a (randomized) chance the Rabbit will either; 1. Tell the player that the donkey is eating hay or, 2. Tell the player to continue along the GRASS & MEADOWS PATH. Further along the GRASS & MEADOWS PATH there’s a (randomized) chance the player will meet Birds(friend/foe) will either; 1. Look in the CAVES for the donkey or, 2. Tell the player to continue along the GRASS & MEADOWS PATH. Further along the GRASS & MEADOWS PATH the player will reach the TAVERN in the KINGDOM. Here the player must return to the beginning and choose a direction once more.
